 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Snack</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Dosirak</li>\n<li>Tea</li>\n<li>Smoothie 과일 스무디</li>\n<li>Fruit</li>\n<li>채소 음료</li>\n<li>닭가슴살</li>\n<li>고구마</li>\n<li>건강즙 (배도라지즙, 양배추즙 등)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"defeats\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#defeats\" aria-label=\"defeats permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Defeats</h2>\n<p>당\n나트륨\n트랜스지방</p>\n<h2 id=\"medicine\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#medicine\" aria-label=\"medicine permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Medicine</h2>\n<p>수면에 좋은 약</p>\n<ul>\n<li>가바, 트립토판. 둘 다 아미노산 성분?</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"etc\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#etc\" aria-label=\"etc permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ETC</h2>\n<p>Big mushroom is so tasty\nBut sasomgi is not tasty i need take care</p>\n<p>마시는 간편식(랩노쉬, 디스이즈푸드)를 하루 종일 먹어도 영양소만 채워진다면 먹어도 되는 것인가?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>소화불량</li>\n<li>장건강</li>\n<li>위건강</li>\n<li>고혈압, 당뇨</li>\n<li>간</li>\n<li>콩팥</li>\n</ul>\n<p>채소섭취를 음료수로 대체해도 효과는 똑같은가?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>섬유질이 제거된 제품이다</li>\n<li>영양속 파괴?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>미네랄</p>\n<h4 id=\"tip\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tip\" aria-label=\"tip permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tip</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>마늘 반 잘라서 전자렌지 20초</li>\n<li>대파 손질해놓으면 사용하기 좋다</li>\n<li>생선구울때 신문지를 덮고 뚜껑을 덮으면 기름이 뚜껑에 안묻어 좋음</li>\n</ul>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I need 2200~2400 kcal (If I want bulk up, 2500~2800)"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"easy-food","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#easy-food","ariaLabel":"easy food permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 